com.b2international.commons.collections

Class UuidLongMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.commons.collections.UuidLongMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class UuidLongMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents a map with UUIDs as keys and values of primitive, non-negative longs. UUIDs are represented internally as a pair of primitive longs as well. Both the MSB and the LSB long parts of the UUID are assumed to be non-zero for all values.
    See Also:
    UUID.variant(), UUID.version()
